HEADWORD: Mastful
<hw>Mast"ful</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See 1st
<er>Mast</er>.]</ety> <def>Abounding in mast; producing mast in
abundance; <as>as, the <ex>mastful</ex> forest; a <ex>mastful</ex>
chestnut.</as></def> <rj><au>Dryden.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
